1. Write a query in SQL to find the name and year of the movies.
select mov_name, mov_year from Movies_Project(code line)
2.Write a query in SQL to find the year when the movie American Beauty
released.
select mov_year from Movies_Project
where mov_name like 'American%'
(SELECT mov_year AS ReleasedYear FROM Movies WHERE mov_name = 'American Beauty')(code when we use like key word, we are intended to get something content which contains coined term)
3. Write a query in SQL to find the movie which was released in the year
1999.
SELECT mov_name FROM  Movies_Project
WHERE mov_year=1999
